reviewText: After awhile this show becomes addicting. I used to watch 7th Heaven (the creater, Brenda Hampton, wrote that and also writes this, Secret Life) and loved it. Then I started watching this and I cant get enough. I ship Ben/Adrian and Ricky/Amy, they are both such perfect couples! I really felt terrible for Ben/Adrian when they lost thier babby and loved when Ricky and Amy slept together aftwards, realizing life is too short not to be 'that' close with someone when you have the chance. Keep the seasons coming, I cant get enough!!!! :)
Title: The Secret Life of the American Teenager: Volume Six
